gh 'ombres\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:US 91st Infantry Division.svg|[[91st Division (United States)|91st Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Wild West Division\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:US 92nd Infantry Division SVG.svg|[[92nd Infantry Division (United States)|92nd Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Buffalo Soldiers\" Division\nFile:US 93rd Infantry Division.svg|[[93rd Infantry Division (United States)|93d Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Blue Helmets\" Division\nFile:US 94th Infantry Division.png|[[94th Infantry Division (United States)|94th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Neuf Cats\" Division{{Clear}}1923\u20131942; 1956\u20131967\nFile:94th Regional Readiness Command SSI.svg|[[94th Infantry Division (United States)|94th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Neuf Cats\" Division{{Clear}}1942\u20131956\nFile:95TrainingDivSSI SVG.svg|[[95th Infantry Division (United States)|95th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Iron Men of Metz\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:96th Infantry Division SSI.svg|[[96th Sustainment Brigade (United States)|96th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"The Deadeye Division\"\nFile:97THID.svg|[[97th Infantry Division (United States)|97th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Trident\" Division\nFile:98th Infantry Division shoulder sleeve insignia.svg|[[98th Division (United States)|98th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Iroquois\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:US 99th Infantry Division.svg|[[99th Infantry Division (United States)|99th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Checkerboard Division\"\nFile:100th Infantry Division SSI.svg|[[100th Division (United States)|100th Division]]{{Clear}}\"Century\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:US 101st Airborne Division patch.svg|[[101st Airborne Division]]{{Clear}}\"Screaming Eagles\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:102 INF DIV SSI.svg|[[102nd Infantry Division (United States)|102nd Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Ozark\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:US 103rd Infantry Division.svg|[[103rd Infantry Division (United States)|103rd Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Cactus Division\"<ref name=\"cmhlist\"/>\nFile:104TrngDivLdrTrngSSI.svg|[[104th Infantry Division (United States)|104th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Timberwolf\" Division\nFile:106th infantry Division.jpg|[[106th Infantry Division (United States)|106th Infantry Division]]{{Clear}}\"Golden Lions\" Division\nFile:108th Infantry.patch.png|[[108th Division (United States)|108th Division]]{{Clear}}\"Golden Griffins\" Division\nFile:US 119th Infantry Division.svg|119th Infantry Division{{Clear}}[[United States Army deception formations of World War II|Operation Wedlock]] \"phantom\" unit\nFile:130 INF DIV SSI.jpg|130th Infantry Division{{Clear}}[[United States Army deception formations of World War II|Operation Wedlock]] \"phantom\" unit\nFile:135 ABN DIV SSI.jpg|135th Airborne Division{{Clear}}\"phantom\" unit\nFile:141 INF DIV SSI.jpg|141st Infantry Division{{Clear}}[[United States Army deception formations of World War II|Operation Wedlock]] \"phantom\" unit\nFile:157 INF DIV SSI.jpg|157th Infantry Division{{Clear}}[[United States Army deception formations of World War II|Operation Wedlock]] \"phantom\" unit\n</gallery>\n\n== Unnumbered ==\n<gallery class=\"center\">\nFile:Panama Canal Div. SSI.jpeg|[[Panama Canal Division (United States)|Panama Canal Division]]<br> 1921\u20131932\nFile:12th Infantry Division SSI.svg|[[Philippine Division]]<br> 1921-1942\nFile:USA - Hawaiian Division.svg|[[Hawaiian Division (United States)|Hawaiian Division]]<br>active 1921\u201341. Basis for 24th and 25th Divisions\n</gallery>\n\n== Cavalry ==\n<gallery class=\"center\">\nFile:1st Cavalry Division - Shoulder Sleeve Insignia.svg|[[1st Cavalry Division (United States)|1st Cavalry Division]]{{Clear}}\"The First Team\"\nFile:US 2nd Cavalry Division.svg|[[2nd Cavalry Division (United States)|2nd Cavalry Division]]\nFile:US 3rd Cavalry Division.svg|[[3rd Cavalry Division (United States)|3rd Cavalry Division]]\nFile:21st cav div.jpg|[[21st Cavalry Division (United States)|21st Cavalry Divisio